      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of peerless quality, this vehicle remains in absolute showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the most exacting standards, it offers an uncompromising aesthetic and mechanical profile for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, serves as a testament to its superior care. We invite serious inquiries to inspect this definitive example of the marque.",
      "price": 48900.0,
