      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-quality specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. This unit has undergone proactive maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive VANOS timing adjustment. The chassis integrity is verified with documented rear subframe reinforcement. Every kinematic component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, maintains factory-spec tolerances. Finished in a flawless coat of Carbon Black Metallic, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal performance.",
